Admin you can make from client.java as he said.

To edit stats go to characters folder.

Search for your name.

In player rights you can change 0 simple person 1 mod 2 admin.

Now scroll down and you see [SKILLS].

And you see a lot of lines like this

character-skill = 0	200	1499734673

That Character-skill = 0 sais which skill that 0 says level and that 1499734673 says the xp.

I always change xp you better change it too.
